{
 "name": "RPlog_Rage_out",
 "title": "Rage Out",
 "summary": "At the New Republic Military Base, the officer Lynae Cassius is found in a disoriented, ground-swapping-with-sky state after what proves to be a small but successful test, with the soldier Mark Steele and concerned troops nearby. Playing the role of an ambassador, Lynae quips for a drink as the worried soldiers offer to help her up and warn that the medics won't allow it, her trembling left hand partly free of its loosened restraint. The brief scene captures the unsettling aftermath of an experiment that went better than Lynae had hoped she would ever need.",
